works.description:
I created and designed a custom website  
for my client Glen Lake.  Charles Schmidt is in the process of attempting 

to take over the company from my client.  During this action he also
hacked  
into my server and stole the website I designed for my client.  I am not  
sure what legal battles Mr. Schmidt and my client are in.  But, Mr.
Schmidt  
DOES NOT own the rights to the site I created because I never passed those
 
rights over to my client. I will be happy to provide all raw files such  
as .fla files, .psd files and other web development files to prove  
ownership and that I created the site.
